½To honour
Thomas J. Johnston of San Francisco
Who visited these gardens as a Commander in the
US Navy during the Normandy Landings and
later with his family and President of his company"خ
ثA Battersea girl with a heart of gold. cared for her parents growing old
She would always give her time to share, with anyone feeling in despair
When troubles seem to fill their day, helped to clear their problems away
The world is now a sadder place, without her kind and smiling face
In memory of Mabel Gladys Coote 1922-2017"د
